Package: ggiraphAlluvial
Type: Package
Title: Interactive Alluvial Geoms for 'ggplot2' Using 'ggiraph'
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: 
    person(
        given = "Andreas",
        family = "Mändle",
        email = "maendle@leibniz-bips.de",
        role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
Description: Provides interactive extensions of alluvial geoms from the
    'ggalluvial' package for use with 'ggiraph'. The package enables
    tooltips, hover effects, and clickable elements for alluvial plots
    created with 'ggplot2', making it easier to explore categorical flow
    data in interactive visualizations.
